messages.main.title: Tabi Tarveler
messages.about.1: We are a young couple from Scotland and Japan and due to being so far apart we need to travel, a lot
messages.about.2: ... and we have fallen in love with it. We both had a passion for photography beforehand.
messages.about.3: But now being able to travel has allowed us to explore new places and culture's through our photography.
messages.about.4: And this is something that we would love to share with everyone.
messages.about.5: We are also available for freelance photography work for small businesses
